---
const { class: className } = Astro.props;
---

<div class:list={["featured-article-container", className]}>
    <h2 class="visually-hidden">Featured Article</h2>
    <article>
        <img src="/images/image-web-3-desktop.jpg" alt="Abstract structures"/>
        <h3>The Bright Future of Web 3.0?</h3>
        <div class="flow">
            <p>We dive into the next evolution of the web that claims to put the power of the platforms back into the people. But is it really fulfilling it's promise?</p>
            <a href="#" class="button">Read more <span class="visually-hidden">The Bright Future of Web 3.0?</span></a>
        </div>
    </article>
</div>

<style lang="scss">
    .featured-article-container {
        container-type: inline-size;
    }

    article {
        display: grid;
        gap: 1rem;

        @container (width > calc(25ch * 2)) {
            gap: 2rem 1rem;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        }

        img {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
        }

        h3 {
            font-size: var(--fs-900);
        }
    }
</style>